item.title: Things that I learned in week 48
item.description: AWS When you’re in doubt about a policy the policy simulator https://policysim.aws.amazon.com should always your first tool of choice. Typescript When unwrapping an object in Typescript the following way, you should be sure that all properties match. If they don’t, they’re just undefinded const { accessKey, accessKeySecret, region, bucket, endpoint } = this.
